title: Preachers of LA S02 Special Part 2 The First Ladies Face Off WEB
description: The First Ladies dish on everything Season One, picking up where they left off at the First Ladies Tea Party They go in hard on Loretta for still being a "single" First Lady. Dominique has a new baby and Myesha has a new body, but nothing's new about their love lives.There's no blushing when these First Ladies give it up, talking about sex, sex, sex!
